2 Sample Quarto Document

2.1 Quarto

Quarto enables you to weave together content and executable code into a finished document. To learn more about Quarto see https://quarto.org. Quarto also allows authors to do literate programming (Erickson, Archer, and Fienen 2024).1

2.2 Running Code

When you click the Render button a document will be generated that includes both content and the output of embedded code. You can embed code like this2:

1 + 1
[1] 2

You can add options to executable code like this

[1] 4

The echo: false option disables the printing of code (only output is displayed).
